pandoc 
  to: html
  output-file: About.html
  standalone: true
  title-prefix: Blogs for my scholarly Observations using ML
  section-divs: true
  html-math-method: mathjax
  wrap: none
  default-image-extension: png
  
metadata
  document-css: false
  link-citations: true
  date-format: long
  lang: en
  editor: visual
  grid:
    sidebar-width: 250px
    body-width: 800px
    margin-width: 250px
    gutter-width: 1.5em
  theme: Darkly
  title: About!
  image: PictureME.jpg
  about:
    template: trestles
    links:
      - icon: twitter
        text: Twitter
        href: 'https://twitter.com'
      - icon: linkedin
        text: LinkedIn
        href: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/heba-nusair-02667b188/'
      - icon: github
        text: Github
        href: 'https://github.com/HebaNu'
